transition is someting when content go one state to another.
llike you can set some hover property.

div {
  background-color: antiquewhite;
  height: 100px;
  width: 100px;
}
div:hover {
  background-color: black;
}

here when you hover it will be instantly black.
after using transition you can control the delay or some style to change.

div {
  background-color: antiquewhite;
  height: 100px;
  width: 100px;
  transition: all 1s ease;
}
in here i used the transition : property,duration,style

